<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="hu">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
    <title>Hiba történt - WebNotes</title>
    <style>
        .error-container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.13);
            border-radius: 10px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            margin-top: 100px;
        }
        .error-code { font-size: 72px; font-weight: bold; color: #f95656; }
        .error-message { font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .back-link {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #1845ad, #23a2f6);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="background">
        <div class="shape"></div>
        <div class="shape"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="header" style="position: relative; top: 20px;">
        <div class="headerTitle">WebNotes</div>
    </div>
    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="error-code">500</div>
        <div class="error-message">Hoppá! Valami hiba történt a szerverünkön.</div>
        <p>Már dolgozunk a hiba kijavításán. Kérjük, próbáld meg később.</p>
        <br>
        <a href="/" class="back-link">Vissza a főoldalra</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>